articles.title: About this blog
articles.description: Some additional details about this blog
articles.contents:
This blog presents some results for the initiative Awake-CameraTrap in wildlife inisights
Most Animal illustrations are coming from phylopic and were elaborated by Gabriela Palomo-Munoz under licence CC-BY-NC 3.0
Most pictures are from the reserves Selva Vides and Escondite in Putumayo and Amargal and Selva Mojada in Choco.
